        "type": "Activity",
        "name": "LES numerical simulation campaign for hemolysis index prediction",
        "activityType": "numerical-simulation",
        "description": "Large-eddy simulation executed in OpenFOAM v9 with a power-law hemolysis transport model. Grid: 42 million cells, time step 1e-5 s, 10 impeller revolutions per operating point. Monte Carlo sampling over 200 viscosity and damage-exponent realisations. No physical prototype was fabricated or tested; all evidence is computational."
      }
    }
